00:35:36,980 --> 00:35:37,690
这个软木塞...
The cork...

413
00:35:39,180 --> 00:35:40,690
就好比这座小岛
is this island.

414
00:35:41,880 --> 00:35:43,580
只有它能够将黑暗势力困在...
And it's the only thing keeping the darkness...

415
00:35:46,300 --> 00:35:47,400
它该在的地方
where it belongs.

416
00:35:55,010 --> 00:35:56,360
那个派你来杀我的男人
That man who sent you to kill me

417
00:35:56,470 --> 00:35:57,940
认为所有人都是堕落的
believes that everyone is corruptible

418
00:35:58,090 --> 00:36:00,390
因为人性本恶
because it's in their very nature to sin.

419
00:36:01,460 --> 00:36:03,220
我把人们引到这岛上来 想证明他是错的
I bring people here to prove him wrong.

420
00:36:04,780 --> 00:36:08,300
一旦他们到了这里 他们的过去就不再重要了
And when they get here, their past doesn't matter.

421
00:36:09,080 --> 00:36:11,040
在你把我的船引到这儿以前 还有过其他人?
Before you brought my ship, there were others?

422
00:36:11,690 --> 00:36:12,850
对 有很多
Yes. Many.

423
00:36:13,060 --> 00:36:15,090
- 他们后来怎么样了?  - 他们都死了
- What happened to them?  - They're all dead.

424
00:36:16,310 --> 00:36:18,450
可如果是你把他们弄来的 你为什么不帮他们?
But if you brought them here, why didn't you help them?

425
00:36:18,560 --> 00:36:20,640
因为我希望他们能自力更生...
Because I wanted them to help themselves...

426
00:36:22,630 --> 00:36:24,480
学会明辨是非
to know the difference between right and wrong

427
00:36:24,630 --> 00:36:25,930
而不是非得由我去告诉他们
without me having to tell them.

428
00:36:26,830 --> 00:36:29,740
如果我强迫他们去做事情 那一切就没意义了
It's all meaningless if I have to force them to do anything.

429
00:36:30,360 --> 00:36:31,560
我为什么非得插手呢?
Why should I have to step in?

430
00:36:31,820 --> 00:36:32,930
你要是不插手 他就会插手啊
If you don't, he will.

431
00:36:44,360 --> 00:36:45,390
你想找个活儿干吗?
Do you want a job?

432
00:36:46,500 --> 00:36:48,370
什么? 找个活儿?
What? A job?

433
00:36:51,770 --> 00:36:52,440
干什么?
Doing what?

434
00:36:53,400 --> 00:36:54,210
嗯...
Well...

435
00:36:54,990 --> 00:36:56,550
如果我不想插手这档子事
If I don't want to step in,

436
00:36:57,700 --> 00:36:59,260
也许你可以替我援助他们
maybe you can do it for me.

437
00:37:00,090 --> 00:37:02,850
你可以做我的... 我的代表...
You can be my... my representative...

438
00:37:03,010 --> 00:37:04,540
做我和那些人的中间人
an intermediary between me and the people

439
00:37:04,630 --> 00:37:07,590
- 那些被我带到岛上的人  - 那 我能换到什么好处?
- I bring to the island.  - Well, what will I get in return?

440
00:37:07,740 --> 00:37:09,510
- 随你说  - 我想要我妻子活过来
- You tell me.  - I want my wife back.

441
00:37:12,930 --> 00:37:13,780
我做不到
Can't do that.

442
00:37:19,220 --> 00:37:22,370
你能赦免我的罪过 让我不用下地狱吗?
Can you absolve me of my sins so I don't go to hell?

443
00:37:22,530 --> 00:37:23,610
这我也办不到
I can't do that either.

444
00:37:30,180 --> 00:37:33,120
那我永远也不想死 我... 我想永生
Then I never want to die. I... I want to live forever.

445
00:37:35,560 --> 00:37:36,230
这个
Now that...

446
00:37:38,600 --> 00:37:39,330
我答应你
I can do.

447
00:38:03,280 --> 00:38:04,610
你让他开口说话了 是吗?
You let him talk to you, didn't you?

448
00:38:10,710 --> 00:38:12,130
他让我给你这个
He told me to give you this.

449
00:38:17,990 --> 00:38:19,830
我想你明白 要是你跟他走
I'm sure you realize that if you go with him,

450
00:38:20,120 --> 00:38:21,430
你就再也见不到你的妻子了
you'll never be with your wife again.

451
00:38:25,310 --> 00:38:26,080
我理解
I understand.

452
00:38:28,350 --> 00:38:30,090
他很擅长...
He can be very...

453
00:38:30,550 --> 00:38:31,320
游说人
convincing.

454
00:38:34,800 --> 00:38:37,100
但我想让你知道 如果你改变主意...
But I want you to know if you ever change your mind...

455
00:38:37,290 --> 00:38:38,570
我是说不论何时...
and I mean ever...

456
00:38:39,900 --> 00:38:41,170
我和你的交易始终有效
my offer still stands.

457
00:38:48,950 --> 00:38:50,050
我有样东西要给你
I have something for you.

458
00:38:54,870 --> 00:38:56,120
你肯定是不小心弄掉了
You must have dropped it.

459
00:38:58,340 --> 00:38:59,310
我在船上找到的
I found it on the ship.

460
00:39:39,340 --> 00:39:40,710

亲爱的 再见了

461
00:40:33,230 --> 00:40:34,200
我改变主意了
I've changed my mind.

462
00:40:40,270 --> 00:40:41,170
你听见了吗?
Are you listening to me?

463
00:40:42,890 --> 00:40:44,080
我改变主意了
I've changed my mind.

464
00:40:50,900 --> 00:40:51,630
我以前错了!
I was wrong!

465
00:40:52,830 --> 00:40:54,130
你说过 我可以改变主意的
You said I could change my mind.

466
00:40:55,660 --> 00:40:56,830
你说过 交易始终有效的!
You said the offer would stand!

467
00:41:00,020 --> 00:41:01,250
那个交易还算数吗?
Does the offer still stand?

468
00:41:03,320 --> 00:41:04,650
那个交易还算数吗?!
Does the offer still stand?!

469
00:41:06,280 --> 00:41:07,530
那个交易还算数吗?!
Does the offer still stand?!

470
00:41:22,740 --> 00:41:23,670
什么交易 老兄?
What offer, dude?

471
00:41:24,580 --> 00:41:27,230
你怎么会在这儿? 你跟踪我?
What the hell are you doing out here? Did you follow me?

472
00:41:27,800 --> 00:41:29,980
- 嗯 差不多  - 走... 走开! 滚!
- Well, kinda.  - Get.. get out! Get out!

473
00:41:30,060 --> 00:41:30,690
喂!
Hey!

474
00:41:30,840 --> 00:41:32,680
- 你没... 你没听见我说的吗?!  - 我只是...
- Did... didn't you hear what I said?!  - Look, I was just...

475
00:41:32,800 --> 00:41:34,910
- 我跟你们的人说了 我什么也不知道!  - 老兄 冷静点!
- I told you people, I don't know anything!  - Dude, just calm down!

476
00:41:35,050 --> 00:41:36,520
- 你干嘛跟踪我?!  - 是你妻子让我来的!
- Why did you follow me?!  - Your wife sent me!

477
00:41:41,110 --> 00:41:41,870
你说什么?
What did you say?

478
00:41:43,030 --> 00:41:46,040
我说 是你妻子让我来的 Isabella啊
I said your wife sent me. Isabella.

479
00:41:48,900 --> 00:41:50,530
她想知道 你为什么把她的十字架埋起来
She wants to know why you buried her cross.

480
00:41:51,850 --> 00:41:53,440
你... 你是怎么知道的?
H... how do you know about that?

481
00:41:54,720 --> 00:41:58,010
- 因为是她刚才告诉我的  - 什么叫 刚才告诉你的?
- Because she just told me.  - What do you mean, just told you?

482
00:41:58,400 --> 00:41:59,830
Isabella看见你把十字架挖出来了 老兄
Isabella saw you dig it up, man.

483
00:42:00,990 --> 00:42:01,970
她现在就站在你身边
She's standing right next to you.

484
00:42:11,960 --> 00:42:13,100

他不相信你

485
00:42:16,910 --> 00:42:19,500

有时候 人们需要点儿时间才会相信

486
00:42:26,280 --> 00:42:27,690
我... 我... 我看不见她
I... I... I don't see her.

487
00:42:29,160 --> 00:42:31,120

告诉他 他英文说得很好

488
00:42:32,100 --> 00:42:33,440
她就在那儿
She's right there.

489
00:42:35,210 --> 00:42:36,730
她说你的英语很棒
She says your English is awesome.

490
00:42:46,210 --> 00:42:47,700

你... 真的在这儿吗?

491
00:42:51,720 --> 00:42:53,220
闭上眼睛
Cierra tus ojos.

492
00:42:53,830 --> 00:42:55,200
她想让你闭上眼睛
She wants you to close your eyes.

493
00:42:58,230 --> 00:42:59,710
没关系的 我会告诉你她说了什么
It's okay. I'll tell you what she says.

494
00:43:09,960 --> 00:43:12,470

No fue tu culpa que yo mor, Ricardo.

495
00:43:13,120 --> 00:43:15,200

我的死不是你的错 Ricardo

496
00:43:16,190 --> 00:43:17,930

就像你非常想救我一样...

497
00:43:19,520 --> 00:43:20,830

只是我的日子到头了

498
00:43:31,420 --> 00:43:33,670

你受了很多苦 Ricardo

499
00:43:37,330 --> 00:43:38,400

我想你...

500
00:43:40,400 --> 00:43:44,350

为了我俩能重聚 我愿意做任何事

501
00:43:45,370 --> 00:43:46,150

我的爱人

502
00:43:48,810 --> 00:43:50,580

我们已经在一起了

503
00:44:08,380 --> 00:44:09,280
她走了?
Is she gone?

504
00:44:11,710 --> 00:44:12,470
嗯
Yeah.

505
00:44:31,850 --> 00:44:32,510
谢谢
Thank you.

506
00:44:34,920 --> 00:44:35,790
嗯 不用客气
Yeah, you got it.

507
00:44:39,230 --> 00:44:40,000
有什么不对劲吗?
Something wrong?

508
00:44:42,720 --> 00:44:44,100
嗯 她还说了一件事
Well, she kinda said one more thing.

509
00:44:45,710 --> 00:44:46,780
一件你非做不可的事
Something you have to do.

510
00:44:48,180 --> 00:44:48,870
什么事?
What?

511
00:44:50,590 --> 00:44:52,370
她说你得阻止那个黑衣人
She said you have to stop the man in black.

512
00:44:53,750 --> 00:44:55,360
你得阻止他离开这座岛
You have to stop him from leaving the island.

513
00:44:56,670 --> 00:44:57,500
因为如果你不这样做...
'Cause if you don't...

514
00:44:59,300 --> 00:45:01,100

我们都会下地狱

515
00:45:44,800 --> 00:45:45,590
早上好
Good morning.

516
00:45:46,070 --> 00:45:46,870
早
Morning.

517
00:45:51,350 --> 00:45:52,500
看来 你收到我的礼物了
I see you got my present.

518
00:45:55,340 --> 00:45:57,620
别沾沾自喜 Jacob 这东西可不是你
Don't gloat, Jacob. It doesn't become you.

519
00:45:59,690 --> 00:46:00,910
所以你想要杀我
So you tried to kill me.

520
00:46:03,080 --> 00:46:04,520
你想要什么 一个道歉?
What do you expect, an apology?

521
00:46:04,650 --> 00:46:05,480
不
No.

522
00:46:06,320 --> 00:46:07,820
我想 我只是好奇你为什么要这么做
I guess I'm just wondering why you did it.

523
00:46:07,970 --> 00:46:08,890
因为我想离开这儿
Because I want to leave.

524
00:46:10,290 --> 00:46:11,690
你就让我走吧 Jacob
Just let me leave, Jacob.

525
00:46:13,120 --> 00:46:15,010
只要我还活着 你哪儿也别想去
As long as I'm alive, you're not going anywhere.

526
00:46:15,120 --> 00:46:16,680
哦 那现在 你知道我为什么想杀你了
Well, then now you know why I want to kill you.

527
00:46:17,370 --> 00:46:18,820
我会杀了你的 Jacob
And I will kill you, Jacob.

528
00:46:19,770 --> 00:46:21,620
就算你杀了我 也会有别人接替我的位置
Even if you do, somebody else will take my place.

529
00:46:21,740 --> 00:46:23,090
哦 那我就把他们也杀了
Well, then I'll kill them, too.

530
00:46:29,700 --> 00:46:30,340
给
Here.

531
00:46:33,300 --> 00:46:34,660
帮你消磨时光
Something for you to pass the time.

532
00:46:40,950 --> 00:46:41,790
回头见
I'll see you around.

533
00:46:48,000 --> 00:46:50,120
再见不会太久的

Sooner than you think.

